sections.heading: by referee; exceptions; report
sections.text: It shall be the duty of the referees to sign any true exceptions taken to any order or decision by them made in the case and return the same with their report to the court making the reference.SourceR.S.1867, Code ยง 303, p. 445;R.S.1913, ยง 7872;C.S.1922, ยง 8817;C.S.192
